{"tid":1092827,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]馬鞍山發生大火災!!!","createTime":"2019-04-05T06:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T08:04:52.000Z","uid":90287,"like":1,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1b4ca1353d9501761976c2f9609a545599078584","tid":1092827,"uid":90287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T06:57:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190401/bkn-20190401162848861-0401_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190401%2Fbkn-20190401162848861-0401_00952_001.html&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJ9xiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=2b65e740\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190401/bkn-20190401162848861-0401_00952_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n內地近日接二連三發生大型奪命工業意外，安徽馬鞍山市周一（1日）再有化工廠爆炸，網傳片段顯示現場不斷冒出火燄及濃煙，幸無人員傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n出事的明遠科技有限公司化工廠位於慈湖高新區，於下午3時許爆炸起火。從片段可見，大火劇烈燃燒，不斷冒出濃煙。當地消防大隊全員出動救火，惟期間仍不時有爆炸聲傳出。據明遠科技初步調查，懷疑是廠內化學材料着火肇禍，現場人員及時疏散，並無傷亡，大火至下午4時38分撲滅。<br />\n<br />\n對於再度發生化工廠事故，令輿論再度質疑工業安全問題。亦有評論指出，其實過往內地的工業意外亦十分頻繁，但現時因傳媒資訊傳遞較快，因此有較多消息傳出。"},{"pid":"355aec7bdb941a8427e93e24f7d8a8e6875e58cf","tid":1092827,"uid":62691,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T07:15:17.000Z","msg":"不安，報驚"},{"pid":"6aaffcd4dee009527c40e0d159ccef0ec33dd649","tid":1092827,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T07:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3f5a4a01a4b45c49c0c1803c2180694dd46986","tid":1092827,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T07:51:01.000Z","msg":"嚇撚到我即刻仆返辦事處，樓主賠返車錢畀我<img src=\"/